# Smart Disaster Relief Resource Allocation System 🚑

An AI-powered solution that predicts disaster severity and optimally allocates relief resources using machine learning and linear programming, with a live dashboard for visualization.

## 🧠 Features
- Cleaned and structured historical disaster dataset
- Predictive modeling for disaster severity
- Resource allocation using linear programming (PuLP)
- Proportional vs optimized allocation strategy comparison
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard

## 📁 Folder Structure
- `Preprocessing/`: Clean & load raw disaster data
- `Features/`: Generate engineered features
- `EDA/`: Visual data analysis
- `Models/`: ML model for severity prediction
- `Optimization/`: Resource allocation logic
- `Dashboard/`: Streamlit app

## ▶️ Run the App
```bash
streamlit run Dashboard/dashboard_app.py
